  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Ylläs Saaga Hotel is offered on half board. The breakfast is buffet style with a range of hot and cold options, served from 7am - 10am. Dinner is three courses with a choice of main, available from 6pm - 7.30pm. </p>
<p>Guests can receive a 30% discount for the <span>à la carte restaurant. Please inform the reception by 6pm the day before. Please note that the à la carte restaurant is not guaranteed to be open all season.</span></p>
<p><span>Guests staying on half board over the New Year will have a New Year's Eve gala dinner included. </span></p>
<p>A Festive Feast is included for all guests arriving before Christmas, for a Christmas celebration meal with games and music. Please note that the Festive Feast replaces the last dinner included in the half-board option <span>or if you’re staying over Christmas the Festive Feast will take place on Christmas day and replace your half-board dinner on this day.</span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
