  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms </strong>sleep two to four people. These rooms have twin beds and an additional sofa-bed suitable for one adult or two children under 12 years old. </p>
<p><strong>Single Room </strong>is sole occupancy of the standard twin room. No single supplement on all dates. These rooms are available on request, please give our Reservations team a call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> sleep two to four people, these rooms have twin beds and an additional double sofa bed - best suited for one adult or two children under 12 years old. Superior rooms also include a small fridge and a kettle. These rooms are available on request, please give our Reservations team a call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Located in the main building</li>
<li>Views of the horizon or fells</li>
<li>Most rooms have a balcony or terrace (not guaranteed)</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bathrobes</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Drying closet</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Most rooms have a balcony or terrace</li>
<li>Most rooms can take a cot</li>
</ul>
<p>For apartment options in this area, check out the <a data-udi="umb://document/d6a5b04bc7044b2faaf1e005d8d9bc7c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d6a5b04bc7044b2faaf1e005d8d9bc7c}" title="Yllas Saaga Apartments">Yllas Saaga Apartments</a>.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
